{"body": "    I don't want to make this kind of method public on my objects.\n\nTechnically you're just hiding the `send` call inside the validation, rather than making it explicit:\n\n```ruby\n  validates :revenue, :inclusion => { :in => ->(r) { r.send(:available_revenues) } }\n\n  protected\n\n  def available_revenues\n    payment.revenue.children\n  end\n```\n\nJust my two cents :), thanks mate.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/7680094", "created_at": "2012-08-12T21:35:51Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7342#issuecomment-7680094", "updated_at": "2012-08-12T21:35:51Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 7342, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/carlosantoniodasilva", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F60b997fd68261ce70cadaf6c8226c042.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/received_events", "gravatar_id": "77237b97a465ae5a293ad323b7296837", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "carlosantoniodasilva", "type": "User", "id": 26328, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/carlosantoniodasilva/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523df5adbd354364b900bcbf"}, "id": 7680094, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/7342"}
